程序包的使用
org.springframework.cglib.core

  • 使用org.springframework.cglib.core的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    org.springframework.cglib.core
    Spring's repackaging of the CGLIB core package (for internal use only).
    org.springframework.cglib.proxy
    Spring's repackaging of the CGLIB proxy package (for internal use only).
  • org.springframework.cglib.core使用的org.springframework.cglib.core中的类 
    类和说明
    AbstractClassGenerator
    Abstract class for all code-generating CGLIB utilities.
    AbstractClassGenerator.ClassLoaderData 
    AbstractClassGenerator.Source 
    KeyFactory
    Generates classes to handle multi-valued keys, for use in things such as Maps and Sets.
    SpringNamingPolicy
    Custom extension of CGLIB's DefaultNamingPolicy, modifying the tag in generated class names from "ByCGLIB" to "BySpringCGLIB".
  • org.springframework.cglib.proxy使用的org.springframework.cglib.core中的类 
    类和说明
    AbstractClassGenerator
    Abstract class for all code-generating CGLIB utilities.
    AbstractClassGenerator.ClassLoaderData
